rows.label: qst100203_msg0002
rows.name:
After they were bashed into submission,
Hiyaya told them that Hiyaya has
another Delta Vessel...

rows.label: qst100203_msg0003
rows.name:
And they went home! Just a
little mumblygrumbling.

rows.label: qst100203_msg0004
rows.name:
Delta Vessel is very useful device
for improve operating efficiency
of Divine Beasts.

rows.label: qst100203_msg0005
rows.name:
All countries very desperate to
make Divine Beasts live even little bit longer.

rows.label: qst100203_msg0007
rows.name:
Hiyaya will try hard to stock
more in future.
